                        <br/><br/><br/><h2>文 献</h2><br><ol><br><li id="R1"><span class='au'>Rowland-Jones, S. L. & Whittle, H. C.</span>: <span class="ti">Out of Africa: what can we learn from HIV-2 about protective immunity to HIV-1?</span> <span class='so'>Nat. Immunol., 8, 329-331 (2007)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17375091" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R2"><span class='au'>Manel, N., Hogstad, B., Wang, Y. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">A cryptic sensor for HIV-1 activates antiviral innate immunity in dendritic cells.</span> <span class='so'>Nature, 467, 214-217 (2010)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/20829794" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R3"><span class='au'>Broz, P. & Monack, D. M.</span>: <span class="ti">Newly described pattern recognition receptors team up against intracellular pathogens.</span> <span class='so'>Nat. Rev. Immunol., 13, 551-565 (2013)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23846113" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R4"><span class='au'>Satoh, T. & Manel, N.</span>: <span class="ti">Gene transduction in human monocyte-derived dendritic cells using lentiviral vectors.</span> <span class='so'>Methods Mol. Biol., 960, 401-409 (2013)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23329503" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R5"><span class='au'>Gao, D., Wu, J., Wu, Y. T. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">Cyclic GMP-AMP synthase is an innate immune sensor of HIV and other retroviruses.</span> <span class='so'>Science, 341, 903-906 (2013)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23929945" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R6"><span class='au'>Li, X. D., Wu, J., Gao, D. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">Pivotal roles of cGAS-cGAMP signaling in antiviral defense and immune adjuvant effects.</span> <span class='so'>Science, 341, 1390-1394 (2013)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23989956" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</sp